The '''Lagulla ice cave'''<ref name="Web" /> was an underwater passage in the [[Naboo Abyss/Legends|core]]<ref name="tpm">{{Film|I}}</ref> of the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]]<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref> [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]].<ref name="tpm" /> In [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]],<ref name="TEA" /> [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and his [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]], [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], along with their navigator, [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]], traveled through this ice cave in a [[Tribubble bongo/Legends|tribubble bongo]] on their journey from [[Otoh Gunga/Legends|Otoh Gunga]] to [[Theed/Legends|Theed]] during the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]].<ref name="tpm" />

